the IDF estimates the number of Palestinians killed at 177, including approximately 120 combatants, 
and the number of injuries including an unspecified number of civilians at 900. Gaza&#8217;s ministry of 
</p>
<p>health estimates the number of Palestinians killed at 189, and persons injured at 1526. No details on 
casualties of civilians are provided by the ministry of health. For IDF figures see Times of Israel, 
