fromhttp://www.saraya.ps/index.php?act=Show&amp;id=24985[Arabic internet edition]. 
</p>
<p> 10 Ezzedeen Al-Qassam Brigades website, available at: http://www.qassam.ps/statement-1469-
For_the_First_Time_Al_Qassam_Brigades_Target_the_Kenesset.html 
</p>
<p> 11 The rule is identified in International Committee of the Red Cross, Customary International 
